  <summary date="2021-03-23T14:45:31Z" status="Introduced in House">Work Opportunities and Resources to Keep Nonprofit Organizations Well Act or the WORK NOW Act 

This bill establishes a grant program for the purpose of providing emergency relief to nonprofit organizations, prioritizing organizations that provide services related to the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic. Organizations receiving funding must use not less than 60% of these funds to hire new employees.</summary>
